                  </hi>. I am shopman to a pawnbroker, in Charlotte-street, New Cut. I have a hat, which was pawned for 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., in the name of T. Baker—the duplicate produced is my writing—I made it out—I do not swear to the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
