                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> His mother had not forbidden him the house—this is my hat—my name is in it—he had not left the house—his father is an embosser, but is very ill, and not expected to live—he was obliged to go into the country for his health, and I believe the prisoner was out of work—his mother is not very well off.</p>
